}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "WUBI-119AGL_V01 109-502-1100" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
WUSB54AG serial numbers appear to start with '''MI2'''.
This device may use U-NII-2 channels but does not implement DFS since it predates the FCC requirements.
